summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from Swan Wagner and Wendla Wagner, his wife, to The City of Seattle, dated November 1st, A. D. 1909, to all that certain tract, lot or parcel of land, situated, lying and being in the County of King, State of Washington, particularly bounded and described as follows, to-wit: All of Lot Number Four (4), in Block Number One (1), in Queen Anne Central Addition to the City of Seattle, that has not been condemned by the City of Seattle for Queen Anne Boulevard, under Ordinance No. 16790 of said City.
